The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Law colleges

 New Delhi, July 12: The Supreme Court has struck down a resolution of the Bar Council of India derecognising LLB courses conducted by evening colleges all over the country. A court refused to uphold the 1999 resolution as the council had not consulted its state counterparts and universities.




